summary: An ordinance providing for the construction of an interceptor sewer in Admiral Way, from a connection with the existing sewer in West Lander Street to the Alley between 61st Avenue Southwest and 62nd Avenue Southwest, and in certain other streets, avenues and alleys, together with the necessary pumping plants, outfall sewers, and force mains, appropriation money therefor from the Cumulative Reserve Fund, and providing for the repayment thereof.
